<plot>The film sketches pre-War Germany and the forces that led to Nazi control and war. Now in the aftermath, German people are faced with choices. They can revert to militarism or embrace peace. They can follow orders or exercise their rights as free citizens. This is a clever piece of propaganda because it invites each viewer to choose his or her own path.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?181162</url></doc>
